Coding practices:

¥ÊLF as newline character
¥ÊUTF-8 encoding
¥ spaces between parentheses and concatenations
	htmlspecialchars ( 'string' . $variable );
¥Êtypecast and sanitize all user input
¥Êuse single quotes for strings and concatenate variables, rather than parsing within double quotes